Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Sands Beach
Description: My favourite spot in Santa Barbara to watch the sunset.

Name: Santa Monica Pier
Description: A famous seaside resort with many shops and cafes, as well as an amusement park and aquarium.

Name: The Oriental Pearl TV Tower
Description: The futuristic TV tower (468 meters high) features a history museum and a revolving restaurant, from which you can enjoy the cityscape.

Name: Jiangsu dafeng elk national nature reserve
Description: Jiangsu dafeng elk national nature reserve is the world's largest elk nature reserve with the largest population of wild elk in the world, and has established the world's largest gene bank for elk.
